import { Component, ViewChild, ElementRef} from '@angular/core'; import { NgbModal } from '@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap'; @Component({ selector: 'app-renuncia', templateUrl: './renuncia.component.html', styleUrls: ['./renuncia.component.css'] }) export class RenunciaComponent { @ViewChild('content', { static: false }) modalContent!: ElementRef; // Definimos una referencia al ElementRef constructor(private modalService: NgbModal) {} openModal() { this.modalService.open(this.modalContent, { centered: true, size: 'lg' }); } }
